---
title: Spicy Kung Pao-Style Chicken with Peanuts and Ginger Rice
description: Juicy pieces of chicken get tossed with crunchy celery and peppers, then flavour-boosted by a quick sweet-savoury sauce in this speedy, spicy stir-fry! The golden peanuts will remind you of classic takeout 'kung pao' chicken!
